dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Map titles: The environment of the city and harbor of Buenos Aires -- Easter Island -- The city and harbor of Rio de Janeiro -- Lima and Callao -- Trinidad and Tobago Islands -- The city and bay of Valparaiso -- The Galápagos archipelago. Running title in margin: Library atlas of the world. [South America detail maps]. 44. From: The library atlas of the world. Chicago, New York : Rand McNally & Co., c1912.
